Quote: The natives who are at present at work on the diggings are fast acquiring a knowledge of gold mining , and some of them are doing exceedingly well. I [Mr. Mackay, jnr.] have been requested by several of them to act as native protector. ... as the natives become more numerous, it will be essential to appoint a person for this purpose.
